Class ProduceCustomersController.TableRow

java.lang.Object
producereportscontrollers.ProduceCustomersController.TableRow
Enclosing class:
ProduceCustomersController
public class ProduceCustomersController.TableRow extends Object
This class is a TableRow for the tables of customers transactions the variables (parameters) of the class are Customer, Orders, Spend all these variables are defining details of our customer transactions the class has a constructor that allows us to set the data through it, we also have getters and setters for each variables as well we use this class mainly to add each instance into a row of the table we have
